            "title": "The Deserted Village",
            "summary": "Here as I take my solitary rounds, Amidst thy tangling walks, and ruined grounds, And, many a year elapsed, return to view Where once the cottage stood, the hawthorn grew – Oliver Goldsmith",
            "content_html": "<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Here as I take my solitary rounds,<br>Amidst thy tangling walks, and ruined grounds,<br>And, many a year elapsed, return to view<br>Where once the cottage stood, the hawthorn grew</p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">– Oliver Goldsmith</p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><figure class=\"wp-image-2567\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/chaos.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 651px) 100vw, 651px\" srcset=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/chaos.png 651w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/chaos.png?w=113&amp;h=150 113w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/chaos.png?w=226&amp;h=300 226w\" alt=\"\" width=\"651\" height=\"864\" data-attachment-id=\"2567\" data-permalink=\"https://unusualcolors.com/2025/08/10/the-deserted-village/chaos/\" data-orig-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/chaos.png\" data-orig-size=\"651,864\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"chaos\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/chaos.png?w=651\"></figure></figure>",
