            "url": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/drinking-song.html",
            "title": "Drinking Song",
            "summary": "Each red petal, A wine-boat, adrift— Raise it, slow, Not to spill What’s left of the day. — inspired by Ge Lifang (d.1164)",
