            "url": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/sunset-over-lake.html",
            "title": "Sunset Over Lake",
            "summary": "A language of loss and renewal, etched in the mist. The willows lean in, trailing ink across the shore. What we remember is always half-shadow, half-dream – The lake holds it all.",
            "content_html": "<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">A language of loss and renewal, etched in the mist.<br>The willows lean in,  trailing ink across the shore.<br>What we remember is always half-shadow, half-dream –<br>The lake holds it all.</p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><figure class=\"wp-image-2550\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/willow.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\" srcset=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/willow.png 720w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/willow.png?w=113&amp;h=150 113w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/willow.png?w=226&amp;h=300 226w\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"956\" data-attachment-id=\"2550\" data-permalink=\"https://unusualcolors.com/2025/07/27/sunset-over-lake/willow/\" data-orig-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/willow.png\" data-orig-size=\"720,956\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"willow\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/willow.png?w=720\"></figure></figure>",
