            "summary": "The mist chills the music notes, wind barely stirs the robe — drenched in dew-light we stand, seeped in silence — inspired by Zhu Dunru (1081-1159)",
            "content_html": "<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The mist chills the music notes,<br>wind barely stirs the robe —<br>drenched in dew-light<br>we stand, seeped in silence</p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">— inspired by Zhu Dunru (1081-1159)</p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><figure class=\"wp-image-2513\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/cold.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\" srcset=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/cold.png 720w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/cold.png?w=113&amp;h=150 113w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/cold.png?w=226&amp;h=300 226w\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"956\" data-attachment-id=\"2513\" data-permalink=\"https://unusualcolors.com/2025/07/13/moon-palace/cold/\" data-orig-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/cold.png\" data-orig-size=\"720,956\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"cold\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/cold.png?w=720\"></figure></figure>",
