        {
            "id": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/five-chinese-verses.html",
            "url": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/five-chinese-verses.html",
            "title": "Five Chinese Verses",
            "summary": "Don’t speak to me of sorghum Red fields, pressed up toward a sky Whatever called to me there Too wild, attempting a face Old verses for my father Dignify the cooling page Black earth is the word it makes Tilts forward, consequential — Wendy Xu",
            "content_html": "<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Don’t speak to me of sorghum<br>Red fields, pressed up toward a sky<br>Whatever called to me there<br>Too wild, attempting a face</p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Old verses for my father<br>Dignify the cooling page<br>Black earth is the word it makes<br>Tilts forward, consequential</p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">— Wendy Xu</p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><figure class=\"wp-image-2500\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/fieldps.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\" srcset=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/fieldps.png 720w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/fieldps.png?w=150&amp;h=150 150w, https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/fieldps.png?w=300&amp;h=300 300w\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"720\" data-attachment-id=\"2500\" data-permalink=\"https://unusualcolors.com/2025/06/15/five-chinese-verses/fieldps/\" data-orig-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/fieldps.png\" data-orig-size=\"720,720\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"fieldps\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://unusualcolors.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/fieldps.png?w=720\"></figure></figure>",
            "image": "https://www.jujubemonster.com/media/posts/52/fieldps.png",
            "author": {
                "name": "Jujube"
            },
            "tags": [
